led tho.  As he threw Hippolyte back into the hut.  Falling to the floor, Hipp pushed herself up and then stood slowely. Grabbing her arms, he slammed her back into the pole and tied her.  &quot;I guess I need to get you fed.  Your no good to me starved.&quot;  <br>
